.SH "Supported elements"
.PP
These elements have been tested with the custom CSS\&.
.SS "Tables"

.PP
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBBasic\fP This theme supports normal markdown tables:
.br
 Item  Title  Description  More  1  Foo  A placeholder  Some lorem ipsum to make this table wider\&.  2  Bar  Also a placeholder  More lorem ipsum\&.  3  Baz  The third placeholder  More lorem ipsum\&.  
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBCentered\fP  A table can be centered with the \fR<center>\fP html tag:
.br
 Item  Title  Description  More  1  Foo  A placeholder  Some lorem ipsum to make this table wider\&.  2  Bar  Also a placeholder  More lorem ipsum\&.  3  Baz  The third placeholder  More lorem ipsum\&.  
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBStretched\fP A table wrapped in \fR<div class="full_width_table">\fP fills the full page width\&.  Item  Title  Description  More  1  Foo  A placeholder  Some lorem ipsum to make this table wider\&.  2  Bar  Also a placeholder  More lorem ipsum\&.  3  Baz  The third placeholder  More lorem ipsum\&.   \fBCaution\fP: This will break the overflow scrolling support!
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBComplex\fP Complex \fRDoxygen tables\fP are also supported as seen in \fBthis example\fP:
.br
 Column 1 Column 2 Column 3 cell row=1+2,col=1cell row=1,col=2cell row=1,col=3 cell row=2+3,col=2 cell row=2,col=3 cell row=3,col=1 cell row=3,col=3 
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBOverflow Scrolling\fP The table content is scrollable if the table gets too wide\&.
.br
 first_column  second_column  third_column  fourth_column  fifth_column  sixth_column  seventh_column  eighth_column  ninth_column  1  2  3  4  5  6  7  8  9  
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBImages\fPA table can contain images:
.br
 Column 1  Column 2    ← the image should not be inverted in dark-mode  
.PP

